Package: constants
Type: Package
Title: Defines some physical constants and functions commonly used in
    optics, plasmonics.
Version: 1.1
Date: 2009-12-20
Author: Baptiste Auguie
Maintainer: Baptiste Auguie <baptiste.auguie@gmail.com>
Description: Physical constants. Gold, silver and glass permittivities,
    together with spline interpolation functions. N and k / epsilon
    conversion both ways. energy/ wavelength conversion. Fano and
    Lorentzian functions, drude model.
License: GPL (>=2)
Depends: R (>= 1.8.0)
URL: http://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/photonics/
LazyLoad: yes

